  "notes_sections": [
    "``loc`` is the lower bound and ``scale`` is the interval width. pdf and ppf deduct ``1 * numel(input)`` FLOPs. cdf deducts ``4 * numel(input)`` FLOPs (composite: sub + div + 2 clip compare/selects, weight 1.0; calibrated alpha 4.0)."
